title: Episode 16 (LIVE): The Stanford Prison Experiment
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: Three psychologists and a poet sit down to watch the 2015 movie, The Stanford Prison Experiment (http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0420293/?ref_=nv_sr_1) in this special LIVE episode of Psychology and Stuff. Drs. Kate Burns, Regan A.R. Gurung, Chuck Rybak, and Ryan Martin chat about the film, the original study, and more.
